                  watchdog_enable PROC
;;;11012  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;11013  void watchdog_enable (void) 
009d08  4993              LDR      r1,|L2.40792|
;;;11014  {
;;;11015  LPC_WDT->WDTC=2000000;
009d0a  05c8              LSLS     r0,r1,#23
009d0c  6041              STR      r1,[r0,#4]
;;;11016  LPC_WDT->WDCLKSEL=0;
009d0e  2100              MOVS     r1,#0
009d10  6101              STR      r1,[r0,#0x10]
;;;11017  LPC_WDT->WDMOD=3;
009d12  2103              MOVS     r1,#3
009d14  7001              STRB     r1,[r0,#0]
;;;11018  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;
009d16  21aa              MOVS     r1,#0xaa
009d18  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;11019  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;
009d1a  2155              MOVS     r1,#0x55
009d1c  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;11020  }
009d1e  4770              BX       lr
;;;11021  
                          ENDP

                  watchdog_reset PROC
;;;11022  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;11023  void watchdog_reset (void) 
009d20  21aa              MOVS     r1,#0xaa
;;;11024  {
;;;11025  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;
009d22  0748              LSLS     r0,r1,#29
009d24  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;11026  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;

009d28  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;11027  }
009d2a  4770              BX       lr
;;;11028  
                          ENDP

                  SysTick_Handler PROC
;;;11034  //***********************************************
;;;11035  void SysTick_Handler (void) 	 /* SysTick Interrupt Handler (1ms)    */

;;;11036  {
;;;11037  //sys_plazma++;
;;;11038  b2000Hz=1;

;;;11044  	}
;;;11045  
;;;11046  if(++t0cnt4>=2)
